.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PAY-LARGEST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-pay-largest \- FEAT-2049 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-pay-largest
.SH DESCRIPTION
node-pay-largest for lightning CLI (FEAT-2049).
.PP
Finds the single largest completed payment by amount_sent_msat from the
listpays output. Returns the amount, payment hash, and destination.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
